I"á	<div class="p">The orchestra of innocence began</div>
<div class="p">To fade in vigor from the ear of man,</div>
<div class="p">Till buzzing like a midge or angry gnat;</div>
<div class="p">From symphonies of tune conducted flat</div>
<div class="p">The pipings of the music leant away,</div>
<div class="p">To join the shadows of a noonlit day.</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Rejoicing in the ritual of form,</div>
<div class="p">Delighted by convention, law, decorum,</div>
<div class="p">Ancestral fathers of this fallen race</div>
<div class="p">Stood meek to heaven, strong in heaven's grace.</div>
<div class="p">The knights of honor, palisades of truth,</div>
<div class="p">Expansively protecting humble couth</div>
<div class="p">Within the wing from barbaric impulse,</div>
<div class="p">The vying knights of darkness to repulse,</div>
<div class="p">Stood dissident to Babel in the height</div>
<div class="p">Of stern, defiant, inelastic right.</div>
<div class="p">O Strength! embracing weakness in thy fold,</div>
<div class="p">How yield to Power, oligarch of old?</div>
<div class="p">How cede dominions of a noble rule</div>
<div class="p">To sotted bureaucrats of Occam's school?</div>
<div class="p">And how, thou Strength, concede the ancient staff?</div>
<div class="p">Cremated piecemeal, with an epitaph</div>
<div class="p">Of scornful merit strewn about thy head,</div>
<div class="p">No bell to warrant thou art soundly dead!</div>
<div class="p">While frantic moderns dance a riot round</div>
<div class="p">To stamp more of thy flesh in rocky ground,</div>
<div class="p">Then rise to thoughts of Epicurean sort,</div>
<div class="p">As foes rejoin a Stoical retort.</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Expansive Might, clutch kingdoms to thy breast;</div>
<div class="p">Mistake in magnitude that thou art blest;</div>
<div class="p">With armies of robotic caliber</div>
<div class="p">Unyielding individuals immure,</div>
<div class="p">Confined by walls of lead or concrete bare,</div>
<div class="p">Or close-packed earth, to dwell therein fore'er.</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; O Egotist! clutch matter in thy fist;</div>
<div class="p">Rub things like salt in ruptures of thy cyst;</div>
<div class="p">Discount the mystery, the central crux,</div>
<div class="p">Then throw thy substance whole into the flux</div>
<div class="p">Of being, with which wholeness thou art one,</div>
<div class="p">For being sovereign, lord of mass become.</div>
